{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Time flies."},{"time":2000,"text":"It's actually almost 20 years ago"},{"time":4000,"text":"when I wanted to reframe the way we use information,"},{"time":8000,"text":"the way we work together: I invented the World Wide Web."},{"time":11000,"text":"Now, 20 years on, at TED,"},{"time":14000,"text":"I want to ask your help in a new reframing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":19000,"text":"So going back to 1989,"},{"time":23000,"text":"I wrote a memo suggesting the global hypertext system."},{"time":26000,"text":"Nobody really did anything with it, pretty much."},{"time":29000,"text":"But 18 months later -- this is how innovation happens --"},{"time":33000,"text":"18 months later, my boss said I could do it on the side,"},{"time":37000,"text":"as a sort of a play project,"},{"time":39000,"text":"kick the tires of a new computer we'd got."},{"time":41000,"text":"And so he gave me the time to code it up."},{"time":44000,"text":"So I basically roughed out what HTML should look like:"},{"time":49000,"text":"hypertext protocol, HTTP;"},{"time":52000,"text":"the idea of URLs, these names for things"},{"time":55000,"text":"which started with HTTP."},{"time":57000,"text":"I wrote the code and put it out there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":59000,"text":"Why did I do it?"},{"time":61000,"text":"Well, it was basically frustration."},{"time":63000,"text":"I was frustrated -- I was working as a software engineer"},{"time":67000,"text":"in this huge, very exciting lab,"},{"time":69000,"text":"lots of people coming from all over the world."},{"time":71000,"text":"They brought all sorts of different computers with them."},{"time":74000,"text":"They had all sorts of different data formats,"},{"time":77000,"text":"all sorts, all kinds of documentation systems."},{"time":79000,"text":"So that, in all that diversity,"},{"time":82000,"text":"if I wanted to figure out how to build something"},{"time":84000,"text":"out of a bit of this and a bit of this,"},{"time":86000,"text":"everything I looked into, I had to connect to some new machine,"},{"time":90000,"text":"I had to learn to run some new program,"},{"time":92000,"text":"I would find the information I wanted in some new data format."},{"time":97000,"text":"And these were all incompatible."},{"time":99000,"text":"It was just very frustrating."},{"time":101000,"text":"The frustration was all this unlocked potential."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103000,"text":"In fact, on all these discs there were documents."},{"time":106000,"text":"So if you just imagined them all"},{"time":109000,"text":"being part of some big, virtual documentation system in the sky,"},{"time":114000,"text":"say on the Internet,"},{"time":116000,"text":"then life would be so much easier."},{"time":118000,"text":"Well, once you've had an idea like that it kind of gets under your skin"},{"time":122000,"text":"and even if people don't read your memo --"},{"time":124000,"text":"actually he did, it was found after he died, his copy."},{"time":127000,"text":"He had written, \"Vague, but exciting,\" in pencil, in the corner."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":132000,"text":"But in general it was difficult -- it was really difficult to explain"},{"time":136000,"text":"what the web was like."},{"time":138000,"text":"It's difficult to explain to people now that it was difficult then."},{"time":140000,"text":"But then -- OK, when TED started, there was no web"},{"time":143000,"text":"so things like \"click\" didn't have the same meaning."},{"time":146000,"text":"I can show somebody a piece of hypertext,"},{"time":148000,"text":"a page which has got links,"},{"time":150000,"text":"and we click on the link and bing -- there'll be another hypertext page."},{"time":154000,"text":"Not impressive."},{"time":156000,"text":"You know, we've seen that -- we've got things on hypertext on CD-ROMs."},{"time":159000,"text":"What was difficult was to get them to imagine:"},{"time":162000,"text":"so, imagine that that link could have gone"},{"time":166000,"text":"to virtually any document you could imagine."},{"time":169000,"text":"Alright, that is the leap that was very difficult for people to make."},{"time":173000,"text":"Well, some people did."},{"time":175000,"text":"So yeah, it was difficult to explain, but there was a grassroots movement."},{"time":179000,"text":"And that is what has made it most fun."},{"time":183000,"text":"That has been the most exciting thing,"},{"time":185000,"text":"not the technology, not the things people have done with it,"},{"time":187000,"text":"but actually the community, the spirit of all these people"},{"time":189000,"text":"getting together, sending the emails."},{"time":191000,"text":"That's what it was like then."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193000,"text":"Do you know what? It's funny, but right now it's kind of like that again."},{"time":196000,"text":"I asked everybody, more or less, to put their documents --"},{"time":198000,"text":"I said, \"Could you put your documents on this web thing?\""},{"time":201000,"text":"And you did."},{"time":204000,"text":"Thanks."},{"time":205000,"text":"It's been a blast, hasn't it?"},{"time":207000,"text":"I mean, it has been quite interesting"},{"time":209000,"text":"because we've found out that the things that happen with the web"},{"time":211000,"text":"really sort of blow us away."},{"time":213000,"text":"They're much more than we'd originally imagined"},{"time":215000,"text":"when we put together the little, initial website"},{"time":217000,"text":"that we started off with."},{"time":219000,"text":"Now, I want you to put your data on the web."},{"time":222000,"text":"Turns out that there is still huge unlocked potential."},{"time":226000,"text":"There is still a huge frustration"},{"time":228000,"text":"that people have because we haven't got data on the web as data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232000,"text":"What do you mean, \"data\"? What's the difference -- documents, data?"},{"time":234000,"text":"Well, documents you read, OK?"},{"time":237000,"text":"More or less, you read them, you can follow links from them, and that's it."},{"time":240000,"text":"Data -- you can do all kinds of stuff with a computer."},{"time":242000,"text":"Who was here or has otherwise seen Hans Rosling's talk?"},{"time":248000,"text":"One of the great -- yes a lot of people have seen it --"},{"time":252000,"text":"one of the great TED Talks."},{"time":254000,"text":"Hans put up this presentation"},{"time":256000,"text":"in which he showed, for various different countries, in various different colors --"},{"time":261000,"text":"he showed income levels on one axis"},{"time":264000,"text":"and he showed infant mortality, and he shot this thing animated through time."},{"time":267000,"text":"So, he'd taken this data and made a presentation"},{"time":271000,"text":"which just shattered a lot of myths that people had"},{"time":274000,"text":"about the economics in the developing world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":278000,"text":"He put up a slide a little bit like this."},{"time":280000,"text":"It had underground all the data"},{"time":282000,"text":"OK, data is brown and boxy and boring,"},{"time":285000,"text":"and that's how we think of it, isn't it?"},{"time":287000,"text":"Because data you can't naturally use by itself"},{"time":290000,"text":"But in fact, data drives a huge amount of what happens in our lives"},{"time":294000,"text":"and it happens because somebody takes that data and does something with it."},{"time":297000,"text":"In this case, Hans had put the data together"},{"time":299000,"text":"he had found from all kinds of United Nations websites and things."},{"time":304000,"text":"He had put it together,"},{"time":306000,"text":"combined it into something more interesting than the original pieces"},{"time":309000,"text":"and then he'd put it into this software,"},{"time":314000,"text":"which I think his son developed, originally,"},{"time":316000,"text":"and produces this wonderful presentation."},{"time":319000,"text":"And Hans made a point"},{"time":321000,"text":"of saying, \"Look, it's really important to have a lot of data.\""},{"time":325000,"text":"And I was happy to see that at the party last night"},{"time":328000,"text":"that he was still saying, very forcibly, \"It's really important to have a lot of data.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":332000,"text":"So I want us now to think about"},{"time":334000,"text":"not just two pieces of data being connected, or six like he did,"},{"time":338000,"text":"but I want to think about a world where everybody has put data on the web"},{"time":343000,"text":"and so virtually everything you can imagine is on the web"},{"time":345000,"text":"and then calling that linked data."},{"time":347000,"text":"The technology is linked data, and it's extremely simple."},{"time":349000,"text":"If you want to put something on the web there are three rules:"},{"time":353000,"text":"first thing is that those HTTP names --"},{"time":356000,"text":"those things that start with \"http:\" --"},{"time":358000,"text":"we're using them not just for documents now,"},{"time":362000,"text":"we're using them for things that the documents are about."},{"time":364000,"text":"We're using them for people, we're using them for places,"},{"time":366000,"text":"we're using them for your products, we're using them for events."},{"time":370000,"text":"All kinds of conceptual things, they have names now that start with HTTP."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374000,"text":"Second rule, if I take one of these HTTP names and I look it up"},{"time":379000,"text":"and I do the web thing with it and I fetch the data"},{"time":381000,"text":"using the HTTP protocol from the web,"},{"time":383000,"text":"I will get back some data in a standard format"},{"time":386000,"text":"which is kind of useful data that somebody might like to know"},{"time":391000,"text":"about that thing, about that event."},{"time":393000,"text":"Who's at the event? Whatever it is about that person,"},{"time":395000,"text":"where they were born, things like that."},{"time":397000,"text":"So the second rule is I get important information back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":399000,"text":"Third rule is that when I get back that information"},{"time":403000,"text":"it's not just got somebody's height and weight and when they were born,"},{"time":406000,"text":"it's got relationships."},{"time":408000,"text":"Data is relationships."},{"time":410000,"text":"Interestingly, data is relationships."},{"time":412000,"text":"This person was born in Berlin; Berlin is in Germany."},{"time":416000,"text":"And when it has relationships, whenever it expresses a relationship"},{"time":419000,"text":"then the other thing that it's related to"},{"time":422000,"text":"is given one of those names that starts HTTP."},{"time":426000,"text":"So, I can go ahead and look that thing up."},{"time":428000,"text":"So I look up a person -- I can look up then the city where they were born; then"},{"time":431000,"text":"I can look up the region it's in, and the town it's in,"},{"time":434000,"text":"and the population of it, and so on."},{"time":437000,"text":"So I can browse this stuff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":439000,"text":"So that's it, really."},{"time":441000,"text":"That is linked data."},{"time":443000,"text":"I wrote an article entitled \"Linked Data\" a couple of years ago"},{"time":446000,"text":"and soon after that, things started to happen."},{"time":450000,"text":"The idea of linked data is that we get lots and lots and lots"},{"time":454000,"text":"of these boxes that Hans had,"},{"time":456000,"text":"and we get lots and lots and lots of things sprouting."},{"time":458000,"text":"It's not just a whole lot of other plants."},{"time":461000,"text":"It's not just a root supplying a plant,"},{"time":463000,"text":"but for each of those plants, whatever it is --"},{"time":466000,"text":"a presentation, an analysis, somebody's looking for patterns in the data --"},{"time":469000,"text":"they get to look at all the data"},{"time":472000,"text":"and they get it connected together,"},{"time":474000,"text":"and the really important thing about data"},{"time":476000,"text":"is the more things you have to connect together, the more powerful it is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":478000,"text":"So, linked data."},{"time":480000,"text":"The meme went out there."},{"time":482000,"text":"And, pretty soon Chris Bizer at the Freie Universitat in Berlin"},{"time":486000,"text":"who was one of the first people to put interesting things up,"},{"time":488000,"text":"he noticed that Wikipedia --"},{"time":490000,"text":"you know Wikipedia, the online encyclopedia"},{"time":493000,"text":"with lots and lots of interesting documents in it."},{"time":495000,"text":"Well, in those documents, there are little squares, little boxes."},{"time":499000,"text":"And in most information boxes, there's data."},{"time":502000,"text":"So he wrote a program to take the data, extract it from Wikipedia,"},{"time":506000,"text":"and put it into a blob of linked data"},{"time":508000,"text":"on the web, which he called dbpedia."},{"time":511000,"text":"Dbpedia is represented by the blue blob in the middle of this slide"},{"time":515000,"text":"and if you actually go and look up Berlin,"},{"time":517000,"text":"you'll find that there are other blobs of data"},{"time":519000,"text":"which also have stuff about Berlin, and they're linked together."},{"time":522000,"text":"So if you pull the data from dbpedia about Berlin,"},{"time":525000,"text":"you'll end up pulling up these other things as well."},{"time":527000,"text":"And the exciting thing is it's starting to grow."},{"time":530000,"text":"This is just the grassroots stuff again, OK?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":532000,"text":"Let's think about data for a bit."},{"time":535000,"text":"Data comes in fact in lots and lots of different forms."},{"time":538000,"text":"Think of the diversity of the web. It's a really important thing"},{"time":541000,"text":"that the web allows you to put all kinds of data up there."},{"time":544000,"text":"So it is with data. I could talk about all kinds of data."},{"time":547000,"text":"We could talk about government data, enterprise data is really important,"},{"time":551000,"text":"there's scientific data, there's personal data,"},{"time":554000,"text":"there's weather data, there's data about events,"},{"time":556000,"text":"there's data about talks, and there's news and there's all kinds of stuff."},{"time":560000,"text":"I'm just going to mention a few of them"},{"time":563000,"text":"so that you get the idea of the diversity of it,"},{"time":565000,"text":"so that you also see how much unlocked potential."}]},{"cues":[{"time":569000,"text":"Let's start with government data."},{"time":571000,"text":"Barack Obama said in a speech,"},{"time":573000,"text":"that he -- American government data would be available on the Internet"},{"time":578000,"text":"in accessible formats."},{"time":580000,"text":"And I hope that they will put it up as linked data."},{"time":582000,"text":"That's important. Why is it important?"},{"time":584000,"text":"Not just for transparency, yeah transparency in government is important,"},{"time":587000,"text":"but that data -- this is the data from all the government departments"},{"time":590000,"text":"Think about how much of that data is about how life is lived in America."},{"time":595000,"text":"It's actual useful. It's got value."},{"time":597000,"text":"I can use it in my company."},{"time":599000,"text":"I could use it as a kid to do my homework."},{"time":601000,"text":"So we're talking about making the place, making the world run better"},{"time":604000,"text":"by making this data available."}]},{"cues":[{"time":606000,"text":"In fact if you're responsible -- if you know about some data"},{"time":610000,"text":"in a government department, often you find that"},{"time":612000,"text":"these people, they're very tempted to keep it --"},{"time":615000,"text":"Hans calls it database hugging."},{"time":618000,"text":"You hug your database, you don't want to let it go"},{"time":620000,"text":"until you've made a beautiful website for it."},{"time":622000,"text":"Well, I'd like to suggest that rather --"},{"time":624000,"text":"yes, make a beautiful website,"},{"time":626000,"text":"who am I to say don't make a beautiful website?"},{"time":628000,"text":"Make a beautiful website, but first"},{"time":631000,"text":"give us the unadulterated data,"},{"time":634000,"text":"we want the data."},{"time":636000,"text":"We want unadulterated data."},{"time":638000,"text":"OK, we have to ask for raw data now."},{"time":641000,"text":"And I'm going to ask you to practice that, OK?"},{"time":643000,"text":"Can you say \"raw\"?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":644000,"text":"Audience: Raw."}]},{"cues":[{"time":645000,"text":"Tim Berners-Lee: Can you say \"data\"?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":646000,"text":"Audience: Data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":647000,"text":"TBL: Can you say \"now\"?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":648000,"text":"Audience: Now!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":649000,"text":"TBL: Alright, \"raw data now\"!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":651000,"text":"Audience: Raw data now!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":653000,"text":"Practice that. It's important because you have no idea the number of excuses"},{"time":657000,"text":"people come up with to hang onto their data"},{"time":659000,"text":"and not give it to you, even though you've paid for it as a taxpayer."},{"time":663000,"text":"And it's not just America. It's all over the world."},{"time":665000,"text":"And it's not just governments, of course -- it's enterprises as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":668000,"text":"So I'm just going to mention a few other thoughts on data."},{"time":671000,"text":"Here we are at TED, and all the time we are very conscious"},{"time":676000,"text":"of the huge challenges that human society has right now --"},{"time":681000,"text":"curing cancer, understanding the brain for Alzheimer's,"},{"time":684000,"text":"understanding the economy to make it a little bit more stable,"},{"time":687000,"text":"understanding how the world works."},{"time":689000,"text":"The people who are going to solve those -- the scientists --"},{"time":691000,"text":"they have half-formed ideas in their head,"},{"time":693000,"text":"they try to communicate those over the web."},{"time":696000,"text":"But a lot of the state of knowledge of the human race at the moment"},{"time":699000,"text":"is on databases, often sitting in their computers,"},{"time":702000,"text":"and actually, currently not shared."}]},{"cues":[{"time":705000,"text":"In fact, I'll just go into one area --"},{"time":708000,"text":"if you're looking at Alzheimer's, for example,"},{"time":710000,"text":"drug discovery -- there is a whole lot of linked data which is just coming out"},{"time":713000,"text":"because scientists in that field realize"},{"time":715000,"text":"this is a great way of getting out of those silos,"},{"time":718000,"text":"because they had their genomics data in one database"},{"time":722000,"text":"in one building, and they had their protein data in another."},{"time":725000,"text":"Now, they are sticking it onto -- linked data --"},{"time":728000,"text":"and now they can ask the sort of question, that you probably wouldn't ask,"},{"time":731000,"text":"I wouldn't ask -- they would."},{"time":733000,"text":"What proteins are involved in signal transduction"},{"time":735000,"text":"and also related to pyramidal neurons?"},{"time":737000,"text":"Well, you take that mouthful and you put it into Google."},{"time":740000,"text":"Of course, there's no page on the web which has answered that question"},{"time":743000,"text":"because nobody has asked that question before."},{"time":745000,"text":"You get 223,000 hits --"},{"time":747000,"text":"no results you can use."},{"time":749000,"text":"You ask the linked data -- which they've now put together --"},{"time":752000,"text":"32 hits, each of which is a protein which has those properties"},{"time":756000,"text":"and you can look at."},{"time":758000,"text":"The power of being able to ask those questions, as a scientist --"},{"time":761000,"text":"questions which actually bridge across different disciplines --"},{"time":763000,"text":"is really a complete sea change."},{"time":766000,"text":"It's very very important."},{"time":768000,"text":"Scientists are totally stymied at the moment --"},{"time":770000,"text":"the power of the data that other scientists have collected is locked up"},{"time":775000,"text":"and we need to get it unlocked so we can tackle those huge problems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":778000,"text":"Now if I go on like this, you'll think that all the data comes from huge institutions"},{"time":782000,"text":"and has nothing to do with you."},{"time":785000,"text":"But, that's not true."},{"time":787000,"text":"In fact, data is about our lives."},{"time":789000,"text":"You just -- you log on to your social networking site,"},{"time":792000,"text":"your favorite one, you say, \"This is my friend.\""},{"time":794000,"text":"Bing! Relationship. Data."},{"time":797000,"text":"You say, \"This photograph, it's about -- it depicts this person. \""},{"time":800000,"text":"Bing! That's data. Data, data, data."},{"time":803000,"text":"Every time you do things on the social networking site,"},{"time":805000,"text":"the social networking site is taking data and using it -- re-purposing it --"},{"time":809000,"text":"and using it to make other people's lives more interesting on the site."},{"time":813000,"text":"But, when you go to another linked data site --"},{"time":815000,"text":"and let's say this is one about travel,"},{"time":818000,"text":"and you say, \"I want to send this photo to all the people in that group,\""},{"time":821000,"text":"you can't get over the walls."},{"time":823000,"text":"The Economist wrote an article about it, and lots of people have blogged about it --"},{"time":825000,"text":"tremendous frustration."},{"time":826000,"text":"The way to break down the silos is to get inter-operability"},{"time":828000,"text":"between social networking sites."},{"time":830000,"text":"We need to do that with linked data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":832000,"text":"One last type of data I'll talk about, maybe it's the most exciting."},{"time":835000,"text":"Before I came down here, I looked it up on OpenStreetMap"},{"time":838000,"text":"The OpenStreetMap's a map, but it's also a Wiki."},{"time":840000,"text":"Zoom in and that square thing is a theater -- which we're in right now --"},{"time":843000,"text":"The Terrace Theater. It didn't have a name on it."},{"time":845000,"text":"So I could go into edit mode, I could select the theater,"},{"time":847000,"text":"I could add down at the bottom the name, and I could save it back."},{"time":852000,"text":"And now if you go back to the OpenStreetMap. org,"},{"time":855000,"text":"and you find this place, you will find that The Terrace Theater has got a name."},{"time":858000,"text":"I did that. Me!"},{"time":860000,"text":"I did that to the map. I just did that!"},{"time":862000,"text":"I put that up on there. Hey, you know what?"},{"time":864000,"text":"If I -- that street map is all about everybody doing their bit"},{"time":867000,"text":"and it creates an incredible resource"},{"time":870000,"text":"because everybody else does theirs."},{"time":873000,"text":"And that is what linked data is all about."},{"time":876000,"text":"It's about people doing their bit"},{"time":879000,"text":"to produce a little bit, and it all connecting."},{"time":882000,"text":"That's how linked data works."},{"time":885000,"text":"You do your bit. Everybody else does theirs."},{"time":889000,"text":"You may not have lots of data which you have yourself to put on there"},{"time":893000,"text":"but you know to demand it."},{"time":896000,"text":"And we've practiced that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":898000,"text":"So, linked data -- it's huge."},{"time":902000,"text":"I've only told you a very small number of things"},{"time":905000,"text":"There are data in every aspect of our lives,"},{"time":907000,"text":"every aspect of work and pleasure,"},{"time":910000,"text":"and it's not just about the number of places where data comes,"},{"time":913000,"text":"it's about connecting it together."},{"time":916000,"text":"And when you connect data together, you get power"},{"time":919000,"text":"in a way that doesn't happen just with the web, with documents."},{"time":922000,"text":"You get this really huge power out of it."},{"time":926000,"text":"So, we're at the stage now"},{"time":929000,"text":"where we have to do this -- the people who think it's a great idea."},{"time":933000,"text":"And all the people -- and I think there's a lot of people at TED who do things because --"},{"time":936000,"text":"even though there's not an immediate return on the investment"},{"time":938000,"text":"because it will only really pay off when everybody else has done it --"},{"time":941000,"text":"they'll do it because they're the sort of person who just does things"},{"time":945000,"text":"which would be good if everybody else did them."},{"time":948000,"text":"OK, so it's called linked data."},{"time":950000,"text":"I want you to make it."},{"time":952000,"text":"I want you to demand it."},{"time":954000,"text":"And I think it's an idea worth spreading."}]},{"cues":[{"time":956000,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":957000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}